<br>
* you severely piss of the mob (throw a couple of nukes, steal its cookies, comment on its fat ass, something like that)<br>
<br>
* you then run away... mob chases you<br>
<br>
* If you are a pet class you then send your pet in, otherwise send your group mates in.<br>
<br>
The trick is to make sure you have enough agro to stop the mob from just turning around and attacking your pet (or group mates). As a cleric I find stuns are good, fear is also good if the mob is unfearable. Not sure what high agro spells a mage has.<br>
<br>
It is also important to make sure both you and your pet can run faster than the mob. Oh and make sure your pet doesnt root it, otherwise your pet gets ganked.<br>
